---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Automation for Candy Manufacturers — Formic"
  description="Labor shortages, overtime, downtime, and missed deliveries. Candy manufacturing is tough — Formic turns sticky challenges into smooth operations. Robotic palletizing and case packing under Full Service Automation."
  ogTitle="Automation for Candy Manufacturers — Formic"
  ogDescription="Fully managed robotic palletizing and case packing for candy manufacturers. No CapEx, deployed in weeks."
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/results/candy" slot="head" />
  <style is:global slot="head">
    .ind-yt-wrap{position:relative;width:100%;max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;aspect-ratio:16/9;background:#000;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
    .ind-yt-wrap iframe{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;border:0}
    .ind-qbox{background:var(--white);padding:34px 32px;border-left:3px solid var(--orange);margin:18px 0 22px}
    .ind-qbox blockquote{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:19px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.5;color:var(--black);margin:0 0 14px;letter-spacing:-.005em}
    .ind-qbox .ind-qattr{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey)}
    .ind-faq{border-top:1px solid var(--lgrey);padding:22px 0}
    .ind-faq:last-child{border-bottom:1px solid var(--lgrey)}
    .ind-faq dt{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:18px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black);margin:0 0 8px}
    .ind-faq dd{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.65;color:var(--mgrey);margin:0}
  </style>

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/results">Results</a><span class="sep">/</span>Candy
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Industry · Candy</div>
    <h1>Automation for <br><em>candy manufacturers</em>.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Labor shortages. Overtime costs. Excess downtime. Missed deliveries. Candy manufacturing is tough. We make it easy to turn sticky challenges into smooth operations.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/stories/taffy-town/1763757449-taffytown-0219.jpg">
        <source src="/Formic-Header.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <span class="dv-cap">Automate NOW · candy</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">$0 CapEx · Deployed in weeks</div>
      <h2>Automate your line. <em>Deploy in weeks</em>.</h2>
      <p>Palletizing and case packing that work from day one. No hiring. No retraining. No headaches. Just consistent output that's smooth as chocolate.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Built for seasonal volume spikes — Halloween, Valentine's, Easter</li>
        <li>Handles high-mix SKUs and packaging changes mid-contract</li>
        <li>Gentle, vision-guided handling for fragile and sticky products</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/contact/get-a-quote" class="larr">Talk to a candy automation engineer →</a>
      <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:18px 0 0"><a href="/downloads/Formic-Best-Practices-Candy-Taffy-Town.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--orange);text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px">↓ Download the candy best practices guide (PDF)</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/taffy-town/1763757449-taffytown-0219.jpg" alt="Taffy Town production floor with Formic palletizing cells" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Candy palletizing · 24/7</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/taffy-town/1741640314-formic-logo-for-taffytown.jpg" alt="Taffy Town and Formic partnership" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Taffy Town · 5.5M lbs of taffy automated</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">Customer story</div>
      <h2>Taffy Town: production speed, consistency, <em>and safety</em>.</h2>
      <div class="ind-qbox">
        <blockquote>"In the long run, if you let equipment do more of the hard stuff and employees do more of the thinking, you're going to have more long-term success, retain employees, and ultimately just put out a better product."</blockquote>
        <div class="ind-qattr">Jason Glade · President &amp; CEO, Taffy Town</div>
      </div>
      <a href="/stories/taffy-town" class="larr">Read the Taffy Town story →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">Taffy Town drives productivity with automation</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(28px,3.4vw,48px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.1;color:var(--white);margin:8px 0 28px;max-width:880px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto">5.5 million pounds of taffy palletized <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">with Formic Full Service Automation</em>.</h2>
    <div class="ind-yt-wrap">
      <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/t-GWPA1uOwQ" title="Taffy Town and Formic" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen loading="lazy"></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px 24px">
    <div class="db-tag">FAQ</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(30px,3.6vw,48px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.06;color:var(--black);margin:8px 0 22px">Candy automation <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">questions</em>.</h2>
    <dl style="margin:0">
      <div class="ind-faq"><dt>Can automation keep up with the high-volume, seasonal spikes in candy production?</dt><dd>Yes. Formic systems are built for surge demand — Halloween, Valentine's, Easter — and run multi-shift to absorb the spike. Formic handles support and maintenance so your internal team stays focused on production.</dd></div>
      <div class="ind-faq"><dt>Will the robots work with our constantly changing SKUs and packaging types?</dt><dd>Flexibility is built in. From mini packs to share bags, single bars to multi-SKU variety packs — quick changeovers between formats, and Full Service lets you swap equipment mid-contract as your line evolves.</dd></div>
      <div class="ind-faq"><dt>We run a wide variety of candy formats. Will automation work for all of them?</dt><dd>Pouches, pillow packs, blister trays, cartons, wrapped bars — every cell is spec'd to product shape, weight, and packaging. Smart programming handles gentle, SKU-specific logic so fragile and sticky products move without damage.</dd></div>
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dgrey">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">Increased production for $0 CapEx? Sweet.</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,56px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.05;color:var(--white);margin:8px 0 28px">Automate your candy lines — <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">for $0 in CapEx</em>.</h2>
    <div class="ind-yt-wrap">
      <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SD0UMnNYR1E" title="Formic Full Service Automation" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen loading="lazy"></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Get started with automation<br><em>today</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="/contact/get-a-quote" class="btn-ctadark">Get a Quote</a>
    <a href="/results" class="btn-ctawh">All Industries</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
